SUMMARY:SNAILS OF THE UNEXPECTED
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:Chaos Theory is a sketch and character group like you have neve
 r seen before! They are four actor/writers – Maria Beadell\, Mikyla Jane 
 Durkan\, Yasser Kayani and Bruce Williams and director/writer Stephen Dinsd
 ale. Between them they have played a puddle in an advert\, worked with Davi
 d Icke\, stripped naked for BBC and Danish TV\, worked with Dario Fo\, been
  the face of British Gas at the Olympics and had material broadcast on BBC 
 TV\, Radio 4 and ITV as well as on film\, the West End and an international
  tour. And ridden a unicycle. Chaos Theory has been going for about five ye
 ars and has played the Edinburgh Fringe\, the Vault Festival\, two Brighton
  Fringes and five Camden Fringes very successfully. Sketches vary from ligh
 t and frothy to dark and disturbing to running for your mum....but in a goo
 d way. And there's music. Always funny! And sketches are quick-fire\, so if
  one doesn't grab you another one quickly will. Among others we have the re
 turn of Brief Encounter\, a witch trial\, a new vers\nMore info: https://co
 medyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/snails-of-the-unexpected/
URL:https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/snails-of-the-unexpected/
